This game was created as a part of my educational process.
In the beginning it had only 2 levels, level one looked almost as same as it is now, the only difference is in background.
Now second level is show as a first bonus level.
When you receive 3 or more achievements you can play bonus level.
Note: this level is too raw and uncompleted. It was added to the game just to show you what kind of game it was at the beginning.
Little scheme of interactions in level 6
If you have any thoughts about this application, just let me know via comments in GooglePlay or via my contact information in \'\'Credits page\'\'.

It\'s your first time you launch this mini-game! I\'m really glad to see you here. This game has simple rules: you just have to feed the cat. You can interact with most items. Also this game has achievements. For now this game supports only English and Russian languages. Default language: English. Have fun playing this game!
